You could just do like this I believe and it would have even less of a chance to cause anything.
```cs
modded class PlayerBase    
{
    overwrite bool CanSprint()
    {
        super.CanSprint();
        ItemBase backpack = FindAttachmentBySlotName("Back");

        if (backpack && backpack.IsHeavyBehaviour())
        {
            return false;
        }
    }
}```

